{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436489472,"sessionID":"ses_316fcb4c5ffehqcHU7q5TvsiXt","part":{"id":"prt_ce90d2d6b002yuwhSddV3njeNp","sessionID":"ses_316fcb4c5ffehqcHU7q5TvsiXt","messageID":"msg_ce90d2546001Gcdvw8wfWXIiKY","type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of what was accomplished across all 3 commits on this branch:\n\n## Summary\n\n### Commit 1: `3be554e` (previously done)\n- **cleanup.ts** — Full JSON support: dry-run and actual cleanup emit structured JSON\n- **verify.ts** — Full JSON support: all paths use output helpers\n- **merge.ts** — Full JSON support: dry-run, no-wave, and result paths\n- **retry.ts** — Full JSON support: all error/dry-run/result paths\n- **resume.ts** — Partial: imports, options, triage console.log guards\n\n### Commit 2: `667f926` (just done)\n- **launch.ts** — Complete JSON support: all `console.log`/`console.error` in `cmdLaunch` entrypoint guarded with `fmt === \"text\"` checks; error paths use `outputError`; dry-run emits structured JSON; preflight cancellation uses `outputMessage`; consolidated `fmt` variable at top of function\n- **resume.ts** — Complete JSON support: interactive resume output, SIGINT handlers, no-tui mode, wave completion dashboard/logs/history all guarded\n\n### Commit 3: `e30a3e8` (just done)\n- **index.ts** — Wired `outputFmt: args.outputFmt` to all 5 remaining operational command calls (`cmdResume`, `cmdVerify`, `cmdMerge`, `cmdRetry`, `cmdCleanup`)\n\n### Verification\n- ✅ TypeScript typecheck passes (`bun run typecheck`)\n- ✅ Build passes (`bun run build`)\n- ✅ Working tree is clean","time":{"start":1773436489472,"end":1773436489472}}}
